{
  "stem": "20580.2",
  "chunk_idx": 13,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You know what this is?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Dirty Jew.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I'm listening to that.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[SPEAKING NON-ENGLISH] And I go up and hide myself.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He takes away the six guys that were there, and the other one they didn't know about it.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Anyway, whatever it is, he was the boss.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I had the keys.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "On the place where they hide it, I know they are on the top. 12:00, 12:30, I went to them.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I had the keys.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I went up them.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We were laying and watching.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "In the front was-- the roof, a little two windows, we see the gypsies.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But the reason we hide it because we are afraid they're going to steal us.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "You know that.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And then comes the death penalty for me.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "There was the second part. 2 o'clock was the death penalty. 5 o'clock I have to go to them.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Everything-- I went to them.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "I went with them till 12 o'clock at night, and I was hiding.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And I was looking.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "They took the pictures from them.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And so they shooed all of them out in the back.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "We was laying in the room.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "Because we're not allowed to be out, 9 o'clock at night.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "We're laying in the room.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "We're laying in the room.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "[NON-ENGLISH] That's all-- five people. 5 o'clock comes from the other people, and they're buried under-- not far from there, they're buried under-- all the 50 people.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And the state-- then comes two of them.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "After the death, after they go, comes two of them.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "This one guy goes-- wants to shoot them.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "[NON-ENGLISH] says no.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "That's finished, [NON-ENGLISH], Ukrainish swine.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "[NON-ENGLISH] --because you have to make an X-ray list, and those two has the picture.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "Put all of this-- [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "Let him go.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "They went away.",
      "word_count": 3
    }
  ],
